@wp.kernel
def expr_fljhit(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = float(0.0)
    v2 = float(1.0)
    tmp = float(0.0)
    tmp = wp.sin(0.89)
    v0 = 0.91
    v2 = (((tmp + 0.59 - v0 + 0.35) - (v2 + 0.87 + tmp + 0.09)) * wp.sin(wp.cos(tmp + 0.09)))
    v1 = v0
    tmp = 0.31
    v0 = v0
    data[tid] = v0
